{"tid":86582,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（絕望）公司欠薪，宜家打唔通電話","createTime":"2017-01-19T07:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T09:21:08.000Z","uid":4204,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ce5f39a994e69508be11afb3ba709b38df49c958","tid":86582,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:46:07.000Z","msg":"我朋友介紹我12月中做推廣員兩日<br />\n我上左佢公司拎左件工作衫同d物品就去商場推銷<br />\n無簽合同 但有畀身份證同銀行卡畀佢地<br />\n到左今個月9號我打畀佢上司問佢幾時出糧<br />\n佢話過幾日<br />\n直到16號我都收唔到<br />\n我再打畀佢佢話聽日到會收到<br />\n17號我都收唔到<br />\n我再打佢佢話18號入 19號會收到<br />\n到左今日19號我都無收到<br />\n我3:00又打畀佢佢佢話搬緊野一陣再打畀我3:20再打畀佢 佢已經無聽我電話<br />\n我就whatsapp佢叫佢盡快覆我或者出糧如果唔係就搵勞工處或者報警<br />\n<br />\n我應該點做？我無簽約同埋薪金大約得一千蚊，勞工處會唔會幫我？"},{"pid":"c7cd13fd94d8302201e1c06aba33d6eae99cdc23","tid":86582,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:46:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4300cdd6c806b1e67c7cde21cc5660ae5f8e8bdd","tid":86582,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲可在幫下手"},{"pid":"60bd565e288a80cfc16df8748e242c201fd423c6","tid":86582,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4279a5d64b907a0386b4ca130d2069630a310cc5","tid":86582,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"揾勞工處"},{"pid":"c216a77e21c628838bd38eed00e7ee6bdc060a11","tid":86582,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"咁少銀碼好心當日做就要求收現金啦<br />\n唉，幫推"},{"pid":"8cbc6963c54a1ae770e1f0e432dbdd94a57f7ca5","tid":86582,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揾勞工處</blockquote><br />\n佢地會唔會因為太少而唔會幫？"},{"pid":"4934c83a1d39bdff8dbb106855d5d85ce0a272de","tid":86582,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T07:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ead8e196a6c9b817e2e5307be649